[[联合国|联合国]]《[[兒童權利公約|兒童權利公約]]》第29條列明教育兒童的目的應是：<ref>{{Cite web|title=儿童权利公约|url=http://www.un.org/chinese/hr/issue/docs/24.PDF|accessdate=2017-07-07|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502162444/https://www.un.org/chinese/hr/issue/docs/24.PDF|archive-date=2019-05-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>
